snippet.title: Labyrinth: The Wizard's Cat | GamePlay PC
snippet.description: Enter the dungeon and help the master wizard to find his cat in this oldschool dungeon crawler. Discover powerful magical items and weapons. Solve puzzles and traps and fight the enemies in this real time combat dungeon crawler game.
